public abstract class CertifiedMessage
extends Message

CertifiedMessage should be extended by messages that need guaranteed delivery to their destination. These messages are sent exactly the same way as other messages, but internally the sender waits for a received receipt certifying the message was received properly. If the resendTimeout lapses before a receipt is received the system will resend the same message without assigning a new unique id.

Author:
Matthew D. Hicks
